                    <p class="text-muted mb-0 px-3">Capture life's moments and personal growth</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Stress Reduction -->
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm text-center py-4 h-100">
                    <i class="bi bi-cloud-sun display-6 text-warning mb-3"></i>
                    <h5 class="fw-bold mb-2">Stress Reduction</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-0 px-3">Express thoughts to reduce anxiety and stress</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Benefits Cards -->
        <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100">
                    <div class="card-body p-4">
                        <h4 class="card-title mb-3"><i class="bi bi-lightbulb text-warning me-2"></i>Journaling Benefits</h4>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled">
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>Improves self-awareness and mindfulness</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>Enhances problem-solving skills</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>Boosts creativity and idea generation</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>Helps achieve personal goals</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>Provides perspective on life events</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100">
                    <div class="card-body p-4">
                        <h4 class="card-title mb-3"><i class="bi bi-star text-primary me-2"></i>Getting Started Tips</h4>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled">
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-arrow-right-circle text-info me-2"></i>Start with just 5 minutes daily</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-arrow-right-circle text-info me-2"></i>Use prompts if you don't know what to write</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-arrow-right-circle text-info me-2"></i>Don't worry about grammar or style</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-arrow-right-circle text-info me-2"></i>Try different formats: lists, stories, or stream-of-consciousness</li>
                            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-arrow-right-circle text-info me-2"></i>Review past entries to see your growth</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- About Section -->
<section id="about" class="py-5 bg-light">
    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
                <h2 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-4">Your Privacy Comes First</h2>
                <p class="lead mb-4">
                    MyJournal is built with privacy as the core principle. Your entries never leave your device.
                </p>
                
                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                    <li class="mb-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-shield-check text-success me-2"></i>
                        <strong>Local Database:</strong> Data stored securely in local SQLite database
                    </li>
                    <li class="mb-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-lock text-success me-2"></i>
                        <strong>Secure Auth:</strong> User accounts with password protection
                    </li>
                    <li class="mb-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-database text-success me-2"></i>
                        <strong>Data Isolation:</strong> Your entries are private to your account
                    </li>
                    <li class="mb-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-download text-success me-2"></i>
                        <strong>Export Control:</strong> Export to PDF or text when you choose
                    </li>
                    <li class="mb-3">
                        <i class="bi bi-eye-slash text-success me-2"></i>
                        <strong>No Analytics Tracking:</strong> We don't track your writing habits
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow-lg">
                    <div class="card-body p-5">
                        <h4 class="card-title mb-4">Why Choose MyJournal?</h4>
                        <div class="d-flex mb-4">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                                <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success fs-4"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex-grow-1 ms-3">
                                <h5>Distraction-Free Writing</h5>
                                <p class="text-muted">Clean interface focused on your thoughts, not ads or distractions.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="d-flex mb-4">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                                <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success fs-4"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex-grow-1 ms-3">
                                <h5>Rich Journaling Tools</h5>
                                <p class="text-muted">Mood tracking, tags, search, and calendar views for meaningful reflection.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="d-flex">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                                <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success fs-4"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex-grow-1 ms-3">
                                <h5>Cross-Device Support</h5>
                                <p class="text-muted">Works on desktop and mobile browsers with consistent experience.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

